{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":12,"day":11}],"page_start":5,"page_end":5,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"头一回","authors":[],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"人物：翻身农奴，男，四十多岁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五六人的藏族民间小乐队。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉：（边唱边上）太阳已经上东山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"急急忙忙把路赶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碰到事情都新鲜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越是琢磨越喜欢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乐队： 什么事让你这么乐呀？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉：（唱）你们不知道呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民主改革那时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万恶领主被咱斗；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分了房子又分地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还给分了一头牛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不再作牛马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不再为人奴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哎哎……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧的制度全摧毁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农奴吐气又扬眉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千年奴隶能翻身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这辈子还是头一回。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说我欢不欢？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说我乐不乐？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乐队：（唱）应该欢！应该乐！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奴隶能唱翻身歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的确这是头一回，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有什么比这更快乐！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉：（唱）跳个翻身舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱支幸福歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（音乐过门）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉：（唱）农民协会当主任，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"普选之后当乡长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"关心群众勤劳动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依靠群众依靠党。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处受尊敬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处受赞扬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千年农奴把家当，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有在这新社会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哎哎……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"管理国家大事情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这辈子还是头一回。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说我欢不欢？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说我乐不乐？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乐队： （唱）应该欢！应该乐！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农奴唱起当家歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的确这是头一回，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有什么比这更快乐！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉： （唱）跳个翻身舞；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱支幸福歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（音乐过门）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉： （唱）党给指出光明路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团结互助搞生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连续五年大丰收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人心里都喜欢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家有余粮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年换新衫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哎哎……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"互助道路放光辉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产粮食没法堆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千年农奴生活好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这辈子还是头一回。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说我欢不欢？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说我乐不乐？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乐队：（唱）应该欢！应该乐！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农奴喜庆好生活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的确这是头一回，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有什么比这更快乐！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉：（唱）跳个翻身舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱支幸福歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（音乐过门）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉：（唱）一个儿子在公学，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个女儿在民族学院，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有一个小儿子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民办小学把书念。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"子女能读书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农奴添慧眼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哎哎……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农奴家中出秀才，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这都是党的恩惠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千年农奴有文化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这辈子还是头一回。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说我欢不欢？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说我乐不乐？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乐队：（唱）应该欢！应该乐！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农奴子女上大学，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的确这是头一回，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有什么比这更快乐！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉：（唱）跳个翻身舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱支幸福歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（音乐过门）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉：（唱）做了一些该做的事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家选我当模范，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我去见毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京城里去参观。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晚上睡不着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里好喜欢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哎哎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天我要去北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我笑在眉头喜在心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农奴去见毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这辈子还是头一回，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说我欢不欢？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说我乐不乐？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乐队：（唱）应该欢！应该乐！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农奴能见毛主席哟！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的确这是头一回，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有什么比这更快乐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉：（唱）哈哈……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头一回！头一回！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农奴翻身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乐队：（唱）头一回。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉：（唱）农奴当家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乐队：（唱）头一回。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉：（唱）连续五年大丰收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乐队：（唱）这辈子咱是头一回。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉：（唱）千年农奴有文化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乐队：（唱）这辈子也是头一回。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉：（唱）如今去见毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乐队：（唱）这辈子还是头一回。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉 乐队：（唱）怎不叫人心欢畅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎不叫人插翅飞！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉：（唱）各位同志请稍待，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回来以后再相会。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（向观众行礼）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"演唱者：索朗旺杰"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}